			Hi! I&apos;m Eduardo.{' '}
			<span
				class="cursor-pointer border-b-2 border-dotted border-gray-900 ease-linear dark:border-gray-100"
				data-rh="Laravel, NodeJs, React"
			>
				Full Stack Developer
